Package: motrack
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Multiple Object Tracking experiments
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jiri", "Lukavsky", , "lukavsky@praha.psu.cas.cz", c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1082-229X"))
  )
Description: For MOT experiments, you need to prepare trajectories, which objects
    later follow. This set of tools helps with random generation of trajectories, 
    visualizing for inspection and adding simple physics like bouncing. 
